languages.text: "Он ждет тебя. Место ты знаешь, будь вовремя. Поворот просматривается от входа в Адептус — смотри, чтоб какие-нибудь зеваки не увидели, куда ты идешь".
"He's waiting for you. You know the place, so be there on time. The turn can be seen from the entrance to the Adeptus — make sure some gawker doesn't see where you're going."

languages.text: “他在等你呢，你知道该去哪里，别迟到。从烈酒修会的入口处可以看到转角，别让那些看热闹的家伙看到你要去什么地方。”
languages.original_text: "He's waiting for you. You know the place, so be there on time. The turn can be seen from the entrance to the Adeptus — make sure some gawker doesn't see where you're going."

traits.locale_text: “他在等你呢，你知道该去哪里，别迟到。从烈酒修会的入口处可以看到转角，别让那些看热闹的家伙看到你要去什么地方。”

languages.text: «Le está esperando. Ya sabe dónde es, así que sea puntual. El giro puede verse desde la entrada del Adeptus, asegúrese de que ningún curioso vea dónde va».
languages.original_text: "He's waiting for you. You know the place, so be there on time. The turn can be seen from the entrance to the Adeptus — make sure some gawker doesn't see where you're going."

traits.locale_text: «Le está esperando. Ya sabe dónde es, así que sea puntual. El giro puede verse desde la entrada del Adeptus, asegúrese de que ningún curioso vea dónde va».

languages.text: 「あの人が待っている。場所は分かるな、遅れずに来い。曲がる場所はアデプトゥスの入り口から見える。行き先を他の連中に見られないように」
languages.original_text: "He's waiting for you. You know the place, so be there on time. The turn can be seen from the entrance to the Adeptus — make sure some gawker doesn't see where you're going."

languages.text: "Er wartet auf Euch. Ihr wisst wo, also seid pünktlich. Man sieht die Stelle vom Eingang des Adeptus aus – achtet darauf, dass kein Gaffer mitkriegt, wohin Ihr geht."
languages.original_text: "He's waiting for you. You know the place, so be there on time. The turn can be seen from the entrance to the Adeptus — make sure some gawker doesn't see where you're going."

languages.text: « Il vous attend. Vous savez où, alors ne soyez pas en retard. Le tournant se voit depuis l'entrée de l'Adeptus, faites bien attention que personne ne remarque où vous allez. »
languages.original_text: "He's waiting for you. You know the place, so be there on time. The turn can be seen from the entrance to the Adeptus — make sure some gawker doesn't see where you're going."

traits.locale_text: « Il vous attend. Vous savez où, alors ne soyez pas en retard. Le tournant se voit depuis l'entrée de l'Adeptus, faites bien attention que personne ne remarque où vous allez. »

languages.text: "Seni bekliyor. Yeri biliyorsun, zamanında orada ol. Döneceğin yer, Adeptus'un girişinden görülüyor. Nereye gittiğinin görülmediğinden emin ol."
languages.original_text: "He's waiting for you. You know the place, so be there on time. The turn can be seen from the entrance to the Adeptus — make sure some gawker doesn't see where you're going."

traits.locale_text: "Seni bekliyor. Neresi olduğunu biliyorsun, zamanında orada ol. Değişim Adeptus'un girişinden görülebiliyor. Birilerinin nereye gittiğini izlemediğinden emin ol."
